        <Parent_String>tòngwǎ [300443537], roofing tile by form [300162673], roofing tile [300010699], tile by function [300444241], tile (material) [300010676], materials by physical form [300247256], materials by form [300014611], materials (substances) [300010358], Materials (hierarchy name) [300010357], Materials Facet [300264091]</Parent_String>
